title: Philippines GDP From Transport
description: GDP from Transport in Philippines increased to 169972 PHP Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 140765 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Transport in Philippines averaged 55216.73 PHP Million from 1998 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 170578 PHP Million in the first quarter of 2022 and a record low of 29949.61 PHP Million in the third quarter of 1998. This page provides the latest reported value for - Philippines Gdp From Transport - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
